{"tid":469278,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁止賣弄性感】胡鴻鈞：有責任的社會企業應該咁做","createTime":"2017-11-15T06:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T14:42:46.000Z","uid":732,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"112e86aecd7d0fb2569383e2ffb6f83f61675da4","tid":469278,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"無綫助理總經理樂易玲向全台藝人發出內部守則，禁止女藝員賣弄性感，出埠要有女同事同行，而劇集只能意識交代強姦或床上情慾戲等情節。胡鴻鈞說：「覺得今次是保護女藝人，讓大家注意成個節目製作，不是集中藝人身材上。（是否有事發生過？）不知道，覺得是一個整體大方向，有責任的社會企業應該咁做，呼籲大家不要集中身材或某一部份，覺得這是好事。（主張減少性感情節？）只要健康為主就無問題。」"},{"pid":"be0e69db9778d93e042e4f54c3264cccc7437466","tid":469278,"uid":55960,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"民智大倒退"},{"pid":"d299f5aa9746161da6b9c7e06a87862d67b4c5ed","tid":469278,"uid":53672,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"最好啦，唔想再見到巫婆比人強姦"},{"pid":"3375040f13c7d070b8b22832ac1d34a988cad144","tid":469278,"uid":2419,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"越黎越似大陸果套"},{"pid":"df5a77db6a8c1ac7f11b98594604652c1e6a2b0d","tid":469278,"uid":55960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越黎越似大陸果套</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48a709f5e1733694b212451c8407a7de40ce063","tid":469278,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"禁止女藝員賣弄性感同禁止不專重國歌一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何謂賣弄?何謂不專重?"},{"pid":"983af1127322c768ffc04dfdc57453f332092da7","tid":469278,"uid":12558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/wingtofp_70341961059a68a278b166.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017